approach :- stair case approach

(ye approach 2D matrix m use hoti h & tb use hoti h jb matrix increasing order m ho )

1. brute force :- 2 loop use kro aur each element ko check kro

2. optimal :- 

a). iske ke top-right / bottom-left cornor se hi start krenge kyoki rem. 2 cornor se particular index ka max & min define nhi hoga

b). yadi top-right cornor ko lenge to index of row = 0 & col = arr[0].length-1 hoga

c). ab curr.-index-value ko target se match krayenge yadi match hoti h to return 'true'

d). yadi value bdi h to next-row m check krenge (row++);

e). yadi choti h to pre-col m check krenge (col--);

